Name: Stack Machines
About the game: Stack Machines is an open-ended puzzle programming game. Use the stack data structure in the form of 4 stack machines moving according to the modules(instructions) placed on a grid to read, transform and output different input sequences. Optimize your solutions for size, module count, speed and cost-effectiveness. Features 4 stacks Wrapping resizable board Open-ended puzzles with a lot of potential for optimization 4 optimization metrics Histograms
